WEBVTT

00:07:59.211 --> 00:08:01.570
Ne disa individe,

00:08:01.570 --> 00:08:03.294
ata mund te kene autizem

00:08:03.294 --> 00:08:05.747
per nje arsye qe eshte gjenetike

00:08:05.747 --> 00:08:09.311
por jo sepse autizmi rrjedh ne familje.

00:08:09.311 --> 00:08:11.690
Dhe arsyeja eshte qe ne disa individe,

00:08:11.690 --> 00:08:14.751
mund te ndodhin ndryshime 
gjenetike ose mutacione

00:08:14.751 --> 00:08:17.794
qe nuk trashegohen nga nena

00:08:17.794 --> 00:08:19.281
apo babai,

00:08:19.281 --> 00:08:22.014
por fillojne krejt te reja tek keta individe.

00:08:22.014 --> 00:08:23.601
mutacione qe jane prezente

00:08:23.601 --> 00:08:25.004
tek veza ose sperma

00:08:25.004 --> 00:08:26.617
ne momentin e konceptimit

00:08:26.617 --> 00:08:28.359
por qe nuk jane trasheguar

00:08:28.359 --> 00:08:31.365
brez pas brezi brenda familjes.